name: Flirty Little Fawn Necklace
description:
This flowery, flirty little fawn is ready for spring adventures! A tiny swarovski crystal for an eye, she hangs from an adjustable sterling silver plated chain with a lobster clasp closure. Every necklace is finished off with a cute heart logo charm at the back and comes packaged in its own clear acrylic case for safe keeping. 

Measurements
Charm is about 1 1/2 inches tall
Chain length adjustable from 16 to 18 inches

Please note pattern placement on each piece may vary due to the hand crafted nature of these jewels. 

Visit us at www.destroyedbydesign.etsy.com for even more adorable jewelry.
